name: Derek McDermott
text: Have some good sandwiches,  got my couple of favorites when i go in there. Customer service is usually good,  and never too packed in there, at least not the times i have been. I dont go here too often, but probably go here again soon. Def not too bad.

name: Tracy Ventresca
text: Went to the one by the west side Shaw's. Service pretty much sucked. They took a half hour to make two subs and they were cold subs. It tasted good but it was pretty much thrown together bc we had waited so long. I do not blame the company bc they do have awesome subs but they really need new employees
